{"tid":1741886,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[有險可守]馬鞍山火燒男子案 夫婦被指在旁講粗口遭起訴","createTime":"2019-11-20T14:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T16:20:43.000Z","uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be1b138aa9b1e8bb22b23d1556a44f8b4dc35573","tid":1741886,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"上周一11.11「三罷」期間，有交通警清早時份於西灣河連開三槍，擊中兩名黑衣示威者，包括一名學生。同日稍後時間，一名男子與黑衣人在馬鞍山廣場對開行人天橋發生爭執，其間男子被人淋潑不明液體及點火，隨即燒傷，送院治理。事隔一周，警方拘捕一對夫婦，指他們旁觀爭執事件期間講粗口，控以在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序行為罪。案件今在東區裁判法院提堂。案件押後至1月29日再訊，以待警方進一步調查，其間批准二人保釋。控方另申請對外將案中事主匿名，辯方提出反對，卻遭裁判官質問：「公眾知情權關你咩事？」最終批准控方申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191120/60287691?fbclid=IwAR3xP5dutIRL1SUc-u61D5B3E02oipLLUMZgvpi81rDnBx7eswl2oC3KJSY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191120%2F60287691%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3xP5dutIRL1SUc-u61D5B3E02oipLLUMZgvpi81rDnBx7eswl2oC3KJSY&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLNeKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=dd850306\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191120%2F60287691%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3xP5dutIRL1SUc-u61D5B3E02oipLLUMZgvpi81rDnBx7eswl2oC3KJSY&h=5ef0a802\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191120/60287691?fbclid=IwAR3xP5dutIRL1SUc-u61D5B3E02oipLLUMZgvpi81rDnBx7eswl2oC3KJSY</a>"},{"pid":"681eb1183d72fcc590f139212264c5872bf83ee5","tid":1741886,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:06:19.000Z","msg":"革命命懸一線 黎明行動刻不容緩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1741862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1741862</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91OjOo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91OjOo.png&h=be7bdec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望聽日可